    {
      "id": "PopularPost77121",
      "post_content": "Pros:  \n-Synergizes with Madness Decks  \n-You get to look at your opponent's hand  \n-You get to choose the cards to be discard (Big difference right there with other discard cards)  \n-You can pick lands  \n  \nCons:  \n-You want to invest cards and mana to make it more effective  \n-[Counterspell](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Counterspell) or any other counters can be devastating. (Yes [Delay](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=132228) will hurt.)  \n-Even if it resolves you still lose card advantage. (Card quality though is entirely different.)  \n   \n2/5  \n  \nAlternatives:  \n[Distress](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Distress) - For BB you get to see your opponents hand and discard 1 non-land card.  \n[Mind Twist](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Twist) and it's Standard Legal counterpart [Mind Shatter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Shatter) - For all your random discarding needs.  \n[Last Rites](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Last Rites) - (Like the PlagueWielder said) You get all the effects for 3 mana only difference is you can't pick land cards which isn't that bad since you still get the Quality > Quantity effect.  \n[Dures](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dures)... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "redcap04",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost77121\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">Pros:<br/>-Synergizes with Madness Decks<br/>-You get to look at your opponent's hand<br/>-You get to choose the cards to be discard (Big difference right there with other discard cards)<br/>-You can pick lands<br/><br/>Cons:<br/>-You want to invest cards and mana to make it more effective<br/>-<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Counterspell\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Counterspell\">Counterspell</a> or any other counters can be devastating. (Yes <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"132228\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=132228\">Delay</a> will hurt.)<br/>-Even if it resolves you still lose card advantage. (Card quality though is entirely different.)<br/> <br/>2/5<br/><br/>Alternatives:<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Distress\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Distress\">Distress</a> - For BB you get to see your opponents hand and discard 1 non-land card.<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mind Twist\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Twist\">Mind Twist</a> and it's Standard Legal counterpart <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mind Shatter\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Shatter\">Mind Shatter</a> - For all your random discarding needs.<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Last Rites\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Last Rites\">Last Rites</a> - (Like the PlagueWielder said) You get all the effects for 3 mana only difference is you can't pick land cards which isn't that bad since you still get the Quality &gt; Quantity effect.<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Dures\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dures\">Dures</a>... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 77121)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '77121'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy22898\">redcap04</span>\r\n                                (6/2/2010 1:15:39 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n